title.narrative: Procurement and logistics for Ebola Care Units in Sierra Leone

description.narrative: This activity (Procurement and logistics for Ebola Care Units in Sierra Leone) is a component of Ebola Care Units in Sierra Leone reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Humanitarian assistance' and a budget of £7,816,314. This component benefits Sierra Leone, and works in the following sector(s): Relief co-ordination and support services. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited, Finnah Holding Company Ltd, International Procurement Agency. The start date is 15-10-2014 and the end date is 14-10-2015.
